      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but honestly i'm super busy this week and the clinic wait times are a nightmare. it doesn't feel like a bone is broken, it just feels really bruised and stiff. if i just keep it elevated and use an ice pack for the next 48 hours, isn't that basically what a doctor would tell me to do anyway?",
