      "content": "i hear you but i'm just really trying to avoid the cost of an x-ray if i don't absolutely need it. like, most people just deal with sprains at home and they're fine eventually, right? if i just take some ibuprofen and do the ice/elevation thing, what's the worst that happens? it's not like i'm going to lose my leg if i wait a couple days to see if the swelling goes down.",
